      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im running a noir detective campaign and need some help with a scene. the crime happened in a pretty rough part of the city, like a heavily crowded neighborhood with a lot of old, decaying apartment buildings, street vendors everywhere, and lots of graffiti. it feels like a place where the police don't really bother to patrol much. based on the vibe of a neighborhood like that, what kind of suspect profile should my detective be looking for to make it feel realistic?",
